Class Playlist<PlayList>

java.lang.Object
group2.mp3player.model.Playlist<PlayList>
Type Parameters:
PlayList - The type representing the playlist.
public class Playlist<PlayList> extends Object
Represents a playlist that contains a collection of songs. The playlist has a name and provides various methods to manage its songs.
